msgid "# Test-ClusterResourceFailure"
msgstr "# 测试集群资源故障"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Simulates a failure of a cluster resource."
msgstr "模拟集群资源发生故障的情况。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `Test-ClusterResourceFailure` cmdlet simulates a failure of a cluster "
"resource."
msgstr "`Test-ClusterResourceFailure` cmdlet 用于模拟集群资源的故障。"

msgid ""
"Based on the failover and failback policies, when this cmdlet runs, the Cluster service moves the\n"
"clustered role, or resource group, and attempts to bring the clustered resource online. This cmdlet\n"
"can be used to simulate what actions the Cluster service will take when a resource fails."
msgstr ""
"根据故障转移和故障恢复策略，当运行此cmdlet时，Cluster服务会移动集群角色或资源组，并尝试将集群资源重新上线。可以使用此cmdlet来模拟资源发生故障时Cluster服务将采取的操作。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Simulate a failure"
msgstr "### 示例 1：模拟故障"

msgid ""
"This example simulates a failure in cluster resource named `Cluster Disk 4`."
msgstr "这个示例模拟了名为“Cluster Disk 4”的集群资源发生故障的情况。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to run this cmdlet. If the input for this parameter is\n"
"`.` or it is omitted, then the cmdlet runs on the local cluster."
msgstr "指定要运行此 cmdlet 的集群的名称。如果该参数的输入值为`.` 或被省略，则 cmdlet 将在本地集群上运行。"

msgid "Specifies the cluster resource of which to simulate failure."
msgstr "指定要模拟故障的集群资源。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster resource of which to simulate failure."
msgstr "指定要模拟故障的集群资源的名称。"

